reviewText: An old film that showcases male strippers auditioning for a sleazy all male extravaganza. Unfortunately, it is a show not worth your while. The production numbers are cheap and the male dancers  are not even good looking.
This is a cheaply made movie, not worth wasting your time on.  I wouldn't recommend this dvd to my worst enemy.

Didn't know what to expect but was totally surprised...some of the dancers are really good and sexy with inventive moves, but the best part is that they all go totally nude and even get interviewed after their dance while standing on stage totally bare ass..lots of male 'junk'. Hope there will be more volumes.
